Minimalistic client for 37signals' Campfire.

Create a ~/.ttyfire:

	yoursubdomain
	your@login.exmpale
	yourpassword

Launch ttyfire:

	./ttyfire "Name of the room"

Dependencies:

	Python 2
	pyfire https://github.com/mariano/pyfire
	GNU bash with readline support
	GNU screen
	Your terminal should support colors
